def remove_duplicates(df): 
    duplicates_before = df['FacilityCode'].duplicated().sum()
    df.drop_duplicates(subset=['FacilityCode'], inplace = True)
    duplicates_after = df.duplicated().sum()
    print("# of Duplicates BEFORE dropping = ", duplicates_before, "\n# of Duplicates AFTER dropping = ", duplicates_after)
    return(df)

var = pca.explained_variance_ratio_

# Cumulative Explained Variance
cum_explained_var = []
for i in range(0, len(pca.explained_variance_ratio_)):
    if i == 0:
        cum_explained_var.append(pca.explained_variance_ratio_[i])
    else:
        cum_explained_var.append(pca.explained_variance_ratio_[i] + 
                                 cum_explained_var[i-1])

print(cum_explained_var)

var = pca.explained_variance_ratio_

# Cumulative Explained Variance
cum_explained_var = []
for i in range(0, len(pca.explained_variance_ratio_)):
    if i == 0:
        cum_explained_var.append(pca.explained_variance_ratio_[i])
    else:
        cum_explained_var.append(pca.explained_variance_ratio_[i] + 
                                 cum_explained_var[i-1])

print(cum_explained_var)
